PRIVACY POLICY
Lokal and it's service providers are committed to protecting your privacy. We use the information you provide to secure your ground transportation reservation using the mobile or web applications. At some point in the future, we may use the information we collect to occasionally notify you about important functionality changes to the mobile app and program. Some of this communication will come via email. However, you will be provided an opportunity in each email to unsubscribe from this list. Lokal does not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to others. Lokal may release account information when we believe, in good faith, that such release is reasonably necessary to (i) comply with law, (ii) enforce or apply the terms of any of our user agreements or (iii) protect the rights, property or safety of Lokal mobile applications, our users, or others.
